Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.28,0:02:18.49,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Where is the truths
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.49,0:02:21.03,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}今無情一帯の世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:23.12,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Here is no truths
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.28,0:02:25.62,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}栄光もなく奪い合う
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.04,0:02:27.96,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}It's like a party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.04,0:02:30.46,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}交錯する者たちよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.67,0:02:32.71,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}突き進め果てるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.71,0:02:34.38,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}勝者と敗者どちらも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.38,0:02:35.51,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}maybe something crazy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.51,0:02:37.72,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}What can I belive?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.88,0:02:40.30,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}そんな問いなんで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.30,0:02:42.43,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}No one answer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.60,0:02:48.64,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}すべてこの虚空の中消えてった
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:53.19,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}今はBREAK OUT BREAK OUT進めよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.36,0:02:54.61,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}CRY OUT CRY OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.61,0:02:59.82,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}その意志を揚げて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:02.82,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}さあもっとBREAK OUT BREAK OUT世界を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.82,0:03:04.08,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}CRY OUT CRY OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:09.37,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}切り開け迷っても
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.37,0:03:12.04,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}So we gatta just go crazy,crazy and mad
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:13.79,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}just go crazy now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.75,0:03:16.80,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}dance,dance crazy ,crazy and mad
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.09,0:03:19.51,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}夢か地獄かGO CRY GO
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.56,0:02:06.56,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}GO CRY GO
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.28,0:02:18.49,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}真理何处寻觅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.49,0:02:21.03,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}眼前这冷酷无情的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:23.12,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}真理无从寻觅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.28,0:02:25.62,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}仅有肮脏的抢与夺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.04,0:02:27.96,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}就像一场派对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.04,0:02:30.46,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}命运纵横交错的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.67,0:02:32.71,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}向着终点一意前行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.71,0:02:34.38,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}无论胜者或败者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.38,0:02:35.51,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}或许某物已然疯狂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.51,0:02:37.72,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}何物可信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.88,0:02:40.30,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}如此疑问为何…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.30,0:02:42.43,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}无人作答
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.60,0:02:48.64,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}一切尽皆消失在这片虚无之中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:53.19,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}现在BREAK OUT BREAK OUT  前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.36,0:02:54.61,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}CRY OUT CRY OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.61,0:02:59.82,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}高举这份决心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:02.82,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}来吧  继续BREAK OUT BREAK OUT突破
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.82,0:03:04.08,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}CRY OUT CRY OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:09.37,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}世界的束缚  即使迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.37,0:03:12.04,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}我们只需变得疯狂  疯而狂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:13.79,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}如今只需变得疯狂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.75,0:03:16.80,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}舞蹈  舞至疯狂  疯而狂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.09,0:03:19.51,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}梦或地狱  GO CRY GO
